<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="margin:0;padding:24px;background:#f4f7fb;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#111827;">
    <div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:18px;padding:32px;">
      <h1 style="margin-top:0;color:#b91c1c;">Confirm account deletion</h1>
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>We received a request to delete your Gulfon account and all associated application data.</p>
      <p>This will permanently delete your user profile, login credentials, categories, expenses, incomes, budgets, and active auth tokens from the application database.</p>
      <p style="margin:24px 0;">
        <a href="<%= deletionUrl %>" style="display:inline-block;background:#b91c1c;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:10px;">Delete My Account</a>
      </p>
      <p>If you did not request this, you can ignore this email.</p>
      <p><a href="<%= deletionUrl %>"><%= deletionUrl %></a></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
